race.comment: OFFA'S DYKE (2) missed the bob here at the latest and is destined to break through soon. Has proven versatile with his speed, so interesting to see what the 3kg claimer does from the wide draw. GAME OVER (10) was good here first-up off 306 days but just lacked fitness. Better for the hitout but may need another one. GRINZINGER GOLD (4) pulled up with excused here last time when well below her best. Drops back in trip off 25 days and can improve sharply. Milnes' booking is a big push. LYRA STAR (13) has switched yards since finishing seventh five weeks ago over 900m at Murray Bridge. Gets in light with the claim and can make his presence felt. DRAGON FISH (6) was good two backhere but struggled last time. Peaking now and is worth keeping safe.
